<% content_for(:main_content) do %>
	<h2> How You Can Help </h2>
	
	<p> Donate money. There are two main ways to donate: by courier and by bank account drop-off. </p>
		
	<p>
		By courier: please send cheques (not cash) to:
		CHEQUE IN THE NAME OF: Angels Orphanage.
		Address to be couriered to:
		Angels Orphanage
		Anath Ashram, Old Cemetery Road
		Shivajinagar Bangalore 51
	</p>
	
	<p>	
		Alternatively, you can directly deposit funds into Angels Orphanages’ account:
		
		To: Angels Orphanage
		
		Bank: State Bank of India/ Infantry Road Branch
		Account number: 30274844 
	</p>
	
	<p>	
		If you would like an income tax rebate form, please include or e-mail your home address along with your donation. 
		
		Drop-Off Donations. Angels Orphanage is open to drop-off donations – just give Sabina a call or send her an e-mail
		 to let her know when to expect you. To see what items the orphanage could use the most, please look at our wish list.
		 Your help is greatly appreciated.
		
		Visit & Volunteer. Our children love meeting new people and making new friends! Angels Orphanage is open on weekdays
		 between 18:00 to 20:00 and on Saturday afternoons for visitors and volunteers. Some past visits that the children 
		really enjoyed include, going out for ice cream with the children, playing board games, having lunch together, and tutoring.
	</p>
